      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ULGmFC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>There is a big difference in price when calculating the gold price without GST and when including GST. This gap between the gold rate without GST and the gold price today with GST rate is what often blindsides shoppers and catches them by surprise!</p>"
