            "faq_question": "How to calculate gold price?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Start by looking at the Gold Rate today without GST. Add 3% GST to that. If you’re opting for jewellery, add the making charges and 3% GST on making charges. In 2025, this will give you the final payable price.</p>"
